Text: RE Im Leaving EnronLuck in your new job I hope you find New England enjoyable I lived in Maine for three years and loved the area and all it had to offer Original Message From mailto Sent Friday March AM To KADDENCOM KADDENCOM Devon Kehoe TomO ernercom Subject Im Leaving Enron judy WPPORG Date Fri Mar MessageID XMIMETrack Serialize by Router on ENEMTAEnronRelease December at PM MIMEVersion Contenttype textplain charsetusascii I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
